署無限期暫停水炮車驗收</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以下COPY AND PASTE <br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2413616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2413616&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=c3fb0715\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2413616</a><br />\n自從反對逃犯條例修訂後，示威和抗爭活動一浪接一浪，至今已爆發出多次激烈的警民衝突，有聲音呼籲警方應使用水炮車（人群管理特別用途車）。不過由於水炮車的威力可以對人造成很大傷害，網絡作家及評論員林鴻達便發起一人一信，要求機電工程署無限期暫停水炮車的驗收工作。<br />\n請LIKE &amp; SHARE 以下FACEBOOK POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MR.JackyHTLim/photos/a.478119468886098/2522140161150675/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMR.JackyHTLim%2Fphotos%2Fa.478119468886098%2F2522140161150675%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=1157b578\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MR.JackyHTLim/photos/a.478119468886098/2522140161150675/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n今日有本地媒體引述消息，指警方引入的水炮車，會在今個星期開始實地測試，最快 8 月中可以使用。林鴻達在帖文表示，有關的檢驗工作將會是由機電工程署負責進行，只要機電署完成相關程序，警務處就能夠正式使用，所以他決定去信機電工程署署長薛永恒。<br />\n<br />\n該封信函大意表示，明白機電署需保持政治中立，但當從香港社會整體利益角度考慮，水炮車可對人生安危造成嚴重禍害。如果機電署停止驗收程序，水炮車便不能出動。相反若完成程序，水炮車有可能造成人道災難，機電工程署將難辭其咎，甚至有可能被國際社會譴責及追究。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，香港社會當前最需要的是喘息下來，緩和民間與政府的對峙局面，重塑相對平和的社會氣氛，尋求解決方法。他認為，薛署長無需根據政府行政指引於 14 日內回覆，而如今關鍵就在機電工程署，懇請薛署長三思。<br />\n<br />\n林鴻達希望網民也能一人一信，所以提供了信函樣本。有網民亦響應呼籲，修改後再寄出。<br />\n<br />\n樣本 ： <a href=\"https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.com/2019/07/LetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html?fbclid=IwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackyhtlim.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F07%2FLetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=e1602fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://jackyhtlim.blogspot.com/2019/07/LetterToEMSDAlfredSit.html?fbclid=IwAR1qbLmZPkwvPa4ajIg-qEULVkGPJVttzpnA6fRv0aYngpMjf_AbIh2DAfQ</a><br />\n<br />\n電郵：alfredsit@emsd.gov.hk<br />\n傳真：2890 7493<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"推入內街玩 等佢啲垃圾車無用武之地 <br />\n<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 多謝車長 按章辦工"},{"pid":"1c6716fcddcac1b7436bc7760f65191d16b86a14","tid":1384773,"uid":69276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4281e640d478ff7f805fe5dfaa535c8dcede02fb","tid":1384773,"uid":139843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:54:46.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"aa1b9eeb19703bf64a9e1ec0335cfc15a096e4c9","tid":1384773,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45a14ca90cbe7209b4bcf81ecb5bfd3f77092f69","tid":1384773,"uid":272177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"已sent"},{"pid":"dcf2cb4c7ed31db5d91ab2f9380d3d5d2f4dc60c","tid":1384773,"uid":269141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ee8ab26ccf1ec675ea56fcc0f498d82fc29e320","tid":1384773,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe7819532bda535b639f0807a28be490d3922eee","tid":1384773,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71f238cb8998aa65e65e5a6c74e35c03d5cd4642","tid":1384773,"uid":63298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d140d4d28b673788